-- Spot Uranium Price Unchanged at $51 a Pound, Ux Consulting Says
-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 2012-03-27T02:26:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/spot-uranium-price-unchanged-at-51-a-pound-ux-consulting-says.html
Uranium-oxide concentrate for
immediate delivery was unchanged at $51 a pound in the week
ended March 26, according to the most-competitive offers tracked
by Ux Consulting Co.  “Unless additional demand emerges over the next several
weeks, the spot market could remain quiet until” the World
Nuclear Fuel Cycle meetings in Helsinki next month, the Roswell,
Georgia-based company said in an e-mailed report today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Sharples in Melbourne at 
